title: 'The bucket is nice; mug is small'
body: Overall build quality of both is nice, but I was surprised to see such a small mug. It is around 500 ml which doesn't serve the purpose of bathing or putting water in plants.

title: 'Nice item'
body: It's a nice bucket of 20 litres with a matching mug.

title: 'Very beautiful and strong bucket.'
body: 'The bucket is very beautiful and strong.'
